<h2 id="lazio">Lazio</h2>

<p><b> Tarquinia </b>
 Etrusque tombs, lamb</p>

<p><b>Rome</b></p>

<p>saltinboca near Trajan column, calzone with ricotta piata navarro, roma tripes, gelato pistacchio 
bought from Treviso and finished on Spanish steps</p>

<h3 id="campania">Campania</h3>

<p><b> Naples </b></p>

<p>calzone  ricotta at “Pizzeria Brandi” and ragu napolitano at “Tandem”.</p>

